attributable to new airplane model mix of $1.2 billion and net reduction of $132 million in other products.   the decline in revenue in 2003 compared to 2002 was primarily due to the decline in the commercial aviation market which resulted in fewer commercial jet aircraft deliveries.   commercial jet aircraft deliveries as of december 31, including deliveries under
