president and chief executive officer of the boeing company. mr. stonecipher has served as chief executive officer since december 1, 2003. he served as vice chairman of the board of
the boeing company from may 2001 until june 2002 and as president and chief operating officer from 1997 until may 2001. he served as president and chief executive officer of mcdonnell douglas corporation (aerospace) from 1994 until its merger with
boeing in 1997. he was chairman of the board, president and chief executive officer of sundstrand corporation (aerospace) from 1991 to 1994. mr. stonecipher is also a director of paccar, inc.
